body:
I run the script provided by@yaroslavvb in #4498, result for `grpc` is 
```
Local rate:       15962.31 MB per second
Distributed rate: 335.68 MB per second
```
and `grpc+verbs` is
```
Local rate:       15514.35 MB per second
Distributed rate: 1306.15 MB per second
```
I'm using a 56Gbps ib network.
